content: I just parked my bike here at Gateshead Interchange and currently have a decent amount of spare spaces available!
A few spaces available at the main campus area of Gateshead College. Just asked and its also a public parking space, not just for students. Cheers :)
Free spaces at Felling Metro station. A bit dodgy tho, make sure you bring your own lockers.
Spaces available at Trinity Square but not much. Seems to be busy for an event nearby.
Just going for a run in the Windhill Mill. Saw loads of spaces available, prolly about 10 something.
